<section class="hero-panel mb-4">
    <span class="eyebrow">Dynamic Route</span>
    <h1 class="display-5 mt-3 mb-3">Hello, <%=Html(displayName)%>.</h1>
    <p class="lead text-secondary mb-0">This page shows a tiny segment-based route handled by `www_starter/default.asp` and rendered through a controller plus view.</p>
</section>

<section class="surface-card p-4">
    <h2 class="h5 mb-3">How it works</h2>
    <p class="mb-2">Route pattern: <code>/hello/{name}</code></p>
    <p class="mb-0 text-secondary">Use this as the reference pattern for small dynamic routes before adding IDs, edit actions, or delete actions.</p>
</section>
